{"tid":2335474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（認真）關於廣州停電，唔係跟車太貼　香港電台今朝辟謠","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T07:01:38.000Z","uid":66087,"like":20,"dislike":232,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"6271261f145f3fd841b974bc953921285743ecbe","tid":2335474,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566404-20201221.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566404-20201221.htm&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=0d807fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566404-20201221.htm&h=d394336a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566404-20201221.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n廣州供電局表示，凌晨零時左右因設備故障，影響廣州三元里、羅沖圍一帶部分用戶用電。局方經過一小時緊急搶修，恢復全部受影響用戶供電。<br />\n<br />\n主題為「廣州冬季停電」的帖文，在微博成熱門搜尋結果，有超過1萬個討論、7000萬個閲讀量。三元里和羅沖圍同屬白雲區，但亦有荔灣區和越秀區市民向本台表示，凌晨出現停電和停水的情況。"},{"pid":"c6198e65575b16ddf47191d4dfe43976d75efd6a","tid":2335474,"uid":66087,"like":11,"dislike":52,"score":-41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:26:52.000Z","msg":"要時刻留意支那消息，但唔好靠Twitter 誤判形勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a055cc6dd72a2956a5cd132572c36810abe92f","tid":2335474,"uid":82640,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"空氣差咗好多<br />\n緊急燒劣質煤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f961d72d8bc469718631d3661b3848e569e97c56","tid":2335474,"uid":155095,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:28:17.000Z","msg":"咁上海今日停電係咪真先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf8ace40884c82da3c89a12483db84995497cc4","tid":2335474,"uid":155431,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"c6198e65575b16ddf47191d4dfe43976d75efd6a","tid":2335474,